10. _If \(\overset{\rightarrow}{A}=2\overset{\rightarrow}{i}-3\overset{\rightarrow}{j}+7 \overset{\rightarrow}{k}\), \(\overset{\rightarrow}{B}=\overset{\rightarrow}{i}+2\overset{\rightarrow}{k}\) and \(\overset{\rightarrow}{C}=\overset{\rightarrow}{j}-\overset{\rightarrow}{k}\) find \(\overset{\rightarrow}{A}\cdot\left(\overset{\rightarrow}{B}\overset{\rightarrow}{ \times}C\right)\)._

